eik_in_the_Second_World_War" title="Schweik in the Second World War">Schweyk in the Second World War</a></i> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Caucasian_Chalk_Circle" title="The Caucasian Chalk Circle">The Caucasian Chalk Circle</a></i> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/Antigone_(Brecht_play)" title="Antigone (Brecht play)">Antigone</a></i> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Days_of_the_Commune" title="The Days of the Commune">The Days of the Commune</a></i> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Tutor_(Brecht)" title="The Tutor (Brecht)">The Tutor</a></i> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/Die_Verurteilung_des_Lukullus" title="Die Verurteilung des Lukullus">Die Verurteilung des Lukullus</a></i> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/Report_from_Herrnburg" title="Report from Herrnburg">Report from Herrnburg</a></i> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/Coriolanus_(Brecht)" title="Coriolanus (Brecht)">Coriolanus</a></i> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/The_Trial_of_Joan_of_Arc_of_Proven,_1431" title="The Trial of Joan of Arc of Proven, 1431">Joan of Arc</a></i> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/Turandot_(Brecht)" title="Turandot (Brecht)">Turandot</a></i> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/Don_Juan_(Brecht)" title="Don Juan (Brecht)">Don Juan</a></i> •</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/Trumpets_and_Drums" title="Trumpets and Drums">Trumpets and Drums</a></i></span></p>
